fields.name: Raleigh Skyline Time Lapse
fields.embed_code:
Raleigh Skyline Time Lapse from Leo Suarez on Vimeo.

My first attempt at making a time lapse video.

I took the pictures in May 2008. I finally found some freeware that can batch resize and create the movie. I hope to make more now that I'm a relatively better photographer and am upgrading my gear.

I really like the cloud movement but the sky transition is awful. That is because I was adjusting the camera settings in manual to try and get more in the photo. The bridge I was standing on also shook every time a car passed by so that is why there is some shake.

fields.name: Venice 2022
fields.rich_description: Venice for Jen's Birthday. The trip included lots of walking around the historic city as well as some boat rides to some of the other islands. The biggest one being Murano. We also took a tran out of Venice into the Treviso region and tried some prosecco.
